title: Alice Cooper--The Nightmare (1975)

Alice Cooper plays Steven, a character from his album Welcome to My Nightmare, who encounters a surreal dream fantasy, guided by the spirit of the nightmare, Vincent Price.
Vintage Cooper + Vincent Price; a spooky, cool, tour through Cooper\&#039;s album \"The Nightmare\" with Alice starting out as emcee, and later...captive of his own dark world.
